originalText.text:
Working out with Jose is LIFE-CHANGING!! I've wanted to write about Jose for some time, but it took a while for me to explain how much his guidance and support mean to me.  Let me start out with the basics:  Working out with Jose is like working out with a very knowledgeable, supportive and motivational friend. He is always on time and ready to greet me with a big smile. In fact, I am running late most mornings because I am a night owl trying to become a morning person, but he is ever so patient with me. He is extremely professional, accommodating and very respectful. Over the last few months working with him, he has helped me become strong in both muscle and spirit. I have sciatica that can be very crippling at times, but he is always ready with modifications and I never experience a flare after working out with him. By the end of every workout, I am always limping, but never too sore to continue. I leave with a feeling of accomplishment and am always excited to come back next time.

I've lost count of how many times I've started and stopped working out in the past. I had personal trainers before, but I never went back more than twice.  I think it's because I always needed someone who was more than a personal trainer, and that is Jose!  He has not only motivated me to find the physical strength I never knew I had, he has also helped me overcome my mental blocks during my worst bouts of depression. He genuinely cares about all of his clients, and he is passionate about helping people find their strength. I am honored to have the privilege of training with him. This is the best investment I've ever made in my whole life, and I hope I can continue to work with him for a long time!  Thank you so much Jose! You are the best!!!!!!

originalText.text: Jose is a gifted coach who blends physical rigor and a soulful approach to helping achieve fitness goals. He supported me in losing weight for my wedding and then training to run and and play tennis. He has a great way of tailoring work outs to your goals, keeping you motivated and sharing a positive perspective through out the process.

originalText.text: I discovered José on line in September 2017 and decided to try him out based on other google reviews.  Very glad I did!  I've now trained with José twice a week since then and he's been absolutely terrific. Highly skilled and professional and very nice too!  He takes a very mindful approach to working with clients.  He listens carefully to your goals and concerns and tailors his approach accordingly. He is always bringing something new to every session from one of the many different disciplines he works in -- including yoga and zoomba both new to me.   I'm in my late fifties and have had numerous trainers over the last two decades many of whom were affiliated with fancy midtown gyms and very good but thanks to José my wife says I'm in my best shape since our wedding day.  I recommend him completely.

originalText.text: I don't normally write reviews but this man deserves all the credit he can receive. Jose Marquez has been helping me built a better me for the past 3 months. While many people focus on the physical changes only, he would focus on the mental and spiritual changes as well. If you are not happy with the way the process is, you won't be happy with the end results. The training is intense but he would converse and try to make the experience enjoyable and informative. Instead of meeting a trainer, you are meeting a friend who is working out with you. Many many times I tried to bargain the workouts chosen. We would discuss the repetitions and the workouts involved. He would even join me in the workouts so that I could finish it. He would always say "we are on this together". Nothing is forced. While many people prefer a harsher method, I appreciated feeling welcomed and heard about what I needed and wanted. He would also track my eating notes and check on me to see what I ate when I didn't send him anything. The workouts are equally effective to any other trainer that only sees physical results as the goal for the client. This man will teach you patience and to love yourself. He is the best!
